cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.DC

This paper presents a machine learning framework for a crowd of smart devices, which involves privacy-preserving techniques and differential privacy guarantees. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) due to the privacy-preserving aspect. The paper also involves data analysis and processing, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the implementation of the system involves distributed computing, which could be categorized under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
